CLARIFICATION (FINAL):
- The eCourts report has multiple columns with "Count" in the header:
  - Column B: "EZ Accounting Count" ← Report type (has other words)
  - Column C: "Inventory Count" ← Report type (has other words)
  - Column D: "Count" ← TOTAL column (EXACTLY "Count" only)

SOLUTION:
- Look for a column header that is EXACTLY "Count" (no other words)
- This is the Total column - exclude it from sum
- Sum all report type columns before it

