- Column B: "EZ Accounting Count" ← NOT exact match, include ✓
- Column C: "Inventory Count" ← NOT exact match, include ✓
- Column D: "Count" ← EXACT match! This is Total ✗ EXCLUDE

Script logic:
- Check B: "EZ Accounting Count" ≠ "Count" → Include
- Check C: "Inventory Count" ≠ "Count" → Include
- Check D: "Count" = "Count" → STOP HERE, exclude this column

